.TH "LIGHTNING-WALLET-META-GET" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-wallet-meta-get \- read a metadata key from the wallet store
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning wallet-meta-get
.I wallet_name key
.SH DESCRIPTION
Reads a key-value entry from the wallet's SQLite meta table.
Returns
.B {"error":"key_not_found"}
if the key does not exist.
.PP
Output: JSON object with wallet, key, value.
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Always.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning-wallet-set-label (1),
.BR lightning-wallet-info-json (1)
